# Secrets - NEVER copy into container
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/credentials*
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/id_rsa*
**/id_ed25519*
**/.ssh/
**/.aws/
**/.gcloud/
**/.azure/

# Git internals
**/.git/

# Node
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/build/

# OS
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Editor
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/

# Docker context (don't recursively include docker files)
**/docker-compose*.yml
**/*.dockerfile
